  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Battery
    Battery is an Items used to increase the max power of a Drone.
    Drone  
    GasTank
    GasTank is an Items used to increase the maximum gas of a Drone.
    Items
    Items is a class for things that can be built in-game, but are not placed on the map like buildings.
    Jetpack
    Jetpack is an Items that increases the movement ability of a Drone, thereby allowing it to travel over mountains, etc.
    ListOfLists
    This method separates the ArrayList of all the ArrayLists of Drones from the MainGame.
    Path
    This method represents a path the drone can take to get from location to another.
    RepairBox
    Repairbox is an Items that increases the max possible repair for a Drone
    Treads
    Treads is an Items that improves a Drone's movement ability, but less so than a Jetpack.
    WeatherBehavior
    This class maintains the behavior of weather on the Map.
